Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------EDCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------OPCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提拔為創設祭執行委員長這一要職的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過著繁忙的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查各社團預算和去年的有沒有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 物品的借用申請收齊沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團的節目幾乎都和去年相同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我想是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要把物品的情況確認好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多 午休有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 向你請教了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一邊 我們的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則是過著寂寞的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然期待少女像以前那樣稱呼自己做教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而事實是少年完全沒有出場的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:28.88,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}邂逅的一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:35.28,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如命中相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:43.11,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要確定這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:47.75,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天依舊陪君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:49.53,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愛上你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:52.56,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:56.58,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心湖泛起陣陣漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:02.05,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻與你一同邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:05.15,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.16,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:10.66,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:14.68,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:19.89,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}宛如夢幻的時間流淌著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:27.79,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}渴望凝望你雙眸中的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:31.85,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.82,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.29,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:43.73,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各社團小攤的內容和去年的差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算跟去年的申請再比對一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 這就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 那時許願了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願我和學長能永遠地在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管明白少女對自己的心意沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:22.09,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\t(0,800,\fs14)\pos(174,249)}中多紗江篇\N\N後篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:22.09,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(174,249)\t(0,800,\fs14)}中多紗江篇\N\N後篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:22.09,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)\pos(174,284)}願 望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:22.09,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(174,284)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)}願 望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是不禁感到心頭一憂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦 真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江忙著執行委員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪老哥這麼閒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江可努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你也做些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也你沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹尖銳的話語在少年心中迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺自己好像距離少女越來越遠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去 我只是個什麼都做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物 笨蛋 又沒能力又色的閒人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用說得這麼絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬眠前的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先把肚子填飽才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 所以我要把你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從少年這時的表情來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計他又在盤算什麼壞主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你要走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還真早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍紀錄片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我緊貼紗江身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把執行委員長的工作情況都錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和我的估計一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定能留作以後的參考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也想試著挑戰紀實類作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 我也想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女 這真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就從今天開始 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 當然了 導演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江 可以再叫我一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 導演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先談談紗江成為執行委員長後的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生以來第一次擔當這麼重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心自己能否做好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢辻 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我們在拍攝創設祭執行委員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把它拍下來留作記錄…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量不要拍我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這間房子怎麼覺得有點冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 工作還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正從上次你教我的地方做起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 別忘了預訂餐飲類小攤用的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我還沒去訂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡快訂好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲了的話可能會買不齊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有時間 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以找其他執行委員幫忙分擔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有向高橋老師諮詢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料的事 我會在今天之內確認好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是少年從未見過的少女的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到這
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥們 好久沒有一起吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人吃多寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒勁 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底現在只有這個陪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗 紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘學長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才紗江她大喊不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是紗江說的夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥對你做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:09:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 昨天很晚才睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想趁午休小睡一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也真是的 說得這麼誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了一會兒已經好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 紗江剛才夢見什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女到底夢見什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年實在是非常在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳部的關東煮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籃球部的炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部做甜酒的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…在同一家店裡購買會比較便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 這想法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和各位部長溝通一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 茶道部那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申請甜酒材料的量跟去年一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 應該是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這由我直接去拜託茶道部…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我去確認好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常完美 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝少女努力的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺自己好像也在一起奮鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年心想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要追加預算？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是距離創設祭還有十天時發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 佈置舞台花費的錢超出了預算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在完全不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就買不了服裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 今年的預算已經比去年增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員長你通融一下 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演劇部要追加預算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有游泳部和茶道部說上年的物品太舊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想申請買新的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是到現在才知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒及時檢查物品情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演劇部的事先放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把物品準備好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是不停犯錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然做不來這麼重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼當時會答應的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員長 有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年心想 沒能幫到少女的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得自己實在是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼唉聲嘆氣的 有什麼煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢辻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟現在的中多一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事情都往自己身上扛而感到焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還為自己是否勝任這份工作而煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢辻也會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會遇到煩惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 能依靠別人的時候就盡量依靠別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要保持非自己解決不可的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘也這樣告訴中多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是擔心中多才來找我商量的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身邊有個擔心自己的人 我好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾句話就得意忘形 這就是少年的壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 少年心想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不僅僅要守在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更要成為紗江的支柱才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這點 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢辻 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點很重要 要好好記住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西想讓紗江你看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這裡用這種顏色怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員長真有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 連這些也拍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直緊跟著紗江 進行貼身採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你遇到煩惱和工作不順時 能向我說出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是 儘管我這人可能很不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望守在你身邊的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能幫上你的一點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有要我幫忙的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那我能拜託你一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…貼身採訪能請你繼續下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我想要你永遠都看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題 紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這段視頻是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店街的服裝出租店給了我們一些舊衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太好了 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 如果這些還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來幫你們做服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員長你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 其實我有縫製禮服的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮服是指那件…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時情急之下騙少年說是媽媽做的那件婚紗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創設祭的日子終於到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時那也是對少女而言很重要的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣佈 輝日東高中創設祭現在正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心燙口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最佳情侶比賽現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請按照出場順序在舞台旁集中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 很好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得紗江你親自請我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也現在幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問 我們符合最佳情侶比賽的主題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金槍子 今年我們一定要得到優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是什麼都可以參加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾我也很想這樣抱抱美也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被紗江成功逆襲了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後百倍奉還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 紗江
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在忙 沒能和學長說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天什麼也沒準備
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下再打開看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我紗江想要的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 一次都沒做過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接…接吻 很久沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再久一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對少女來說 這就是最好的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:29.22,in,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}{\pos(320,235)}8年後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢面具 超級高能射線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輸 蚱蜢面具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小寶寶也在為蚱蜢面具加油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟少年以及家人一起高興地去看英雄舞台秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是少女那天在神社許下的另一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們能永遠像這樣地恩愛下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由衷地為他們祈禱著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:34.46,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}清晨傳來腳踏車的清脆鈴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:39.94,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}彷彿告訴著我時間逐漸流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.05,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這份無法消散的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:51.09,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定決心把它交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:23:03.12,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}點綴未來的預想於我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:09.47,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}暗自祈禱當中有你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:14.28,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}於深秋落葉時深呼吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:22.03,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}嘴裡吐出的卻是絲絲的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:29.53,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}現在只希望你能聽我說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:32.58,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:36.36,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這便是我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集終於到我出場了 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 森島學姐你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 讓人家等那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓我期待之後發生的各種事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種事是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種事就是這樣的那樣的事囉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些話別讓女孩子說出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:23:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一聽就知道是個用不著解釋的標題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家準備好沒？
